{"tid":1854985,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國科學院發現 中成藥「雙黃連口服液」可抑制新型冠狀病毒。消息傳出後，多個網上平台售罄","createTime":"2020-01-31T20:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T01:49:22.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"45c837ada5debddc7237d703cb4963678bf1a4c7","tid":1854985,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:00:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505980-20200201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505980-20200201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMVuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=78d2412d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505980-20200201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=27d755f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505980-20200201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a> <br />\n中國科學院上海藥物所及武漢病毒所聯合研究初步發現，中成藥「雙黃連口服液」可抑制新型冠狀病毒。消息傳出後，多個網上平台的「雙黃連口服液」，都已經售罄或下架。<br />\n<br />\n「雙黃連口服液」由金銀花、黃芩及連翹三款中藥組成，中醫認為，這三款中藥具有清熱解毒、表裡雙清的作用。現代醫學研究認為，「雙黃連口服液」具有抗病毒、抑菌、提高免疫功能的作用，是目前有效的抗病毒藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n上海藥物所長期從事抗病毒藥物研究，2003年沙士期間，曾率先證實「雙黃連口服液」具有抗沙士病毒的作用，十多年來亦陸續證實「雙黃連口服液」對流感病毒、沙士及中東呼吸綜合症病毒，具有明顯的抗病毒效應。"},{"pid":"c6921e83c5257ec66a41948539bb0f4ec7d9dd33","tid":1854985,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9eb2d0378223cae548c021cf143d87d4b920c1","tid":1854985,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:02:01.000Z","msg":"巫醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d7f10aa9071b734c5e2d7cfe2217723e4a4c45","tid":1854985,"uid":186543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:02:47.000Z","msg":"1652！"},{"pid":"01e49a44d896941c5429cc04f2c8bcf96fc4e2a5","tid":1854985,"uid":196329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:03:26.000Z","msg":"一方面蠢撚繼續搶<br />\n但大陸各大論壇已經狂屌呢單野係板藍根2.0<br />\n各所謂中科園以前d研究全部都係9up<br />\n連支付寶都出黎話人民日報個報道係謠言"},{"pid":"214d7affd5a7d1c5b6683c6dc669f228cf98801f","tid":1854985,"uid":122710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:04:18.000Z","msg":"用呢個做回血命<br />\n都可以回幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0862361b53b0f9190f2f0a56fe341fe4b305fcd","tid":1854985,"uid":122710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用呢個做回血劍<br />\n都可以回幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c6e4ea5051c36cd6b9d1002ddb22e3e8ebe8026a","tid":1854985,"uid":1224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:06:37.000Z","msg":"雙黃連口服精液 我大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02af797521d515719b25552402fb6e6028161ae","tid":1854985,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea348769168a3de7c8c709fda34f7bee8c10e40","tid":1854985,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:10:27.000Z","msg":"國家有藥醫了，無漢佬同藍屍快快返歸買藥啦"},{"pid":"605b41153e7e58d6e9864ef5e1ae5711edb34aa9","tid":1854985,"uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:19:29.